snippet.title: Monster Collector VR - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Monster Collector VR is going to be released as early access on Feb 19, 2021 
Available on steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1423090/Monster_Collector/
Join our discord:
https://discord.gg/4jNqWXy

Monster Collector is a physics based VR melee combat game. You can fight all kinds of unique monsters in the sandbox. Dragons, Demons, Mythological Creatures. Each creature can bring you different experience. You can tear them apart, slice them to half.
